---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About — MIIKEY" description="A little bit about me." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1.5rem;">

      <h1 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 2rem;">About</h1>

      <div class="prose" style="font-size: 0.975rem; color: var(--fg); line-height: 1.85;">
        <p>
          Hey, I'm MIIKEY. I build things on the internet — mostly in the crypto and DeFi space.
          I've contributed to protocols like Aave, worked on DeFi analytics tools, and spent a lot of
          time thinking about how decentralized finance reshapes ownership and access.
        </p>
        <p>
          I care about open systems, good UX, and building products that actually work.
          This site is where I share what I'm thinking about, what I'm building, and what I'm learning.
        </p>
        <p>
          If something on here resonates with you, feel free to reach out.
        </p>

        <h2>Now</h2>
        <p>
          Currently exploring DeFi infrastructure, tokenization of real-world assets,
          and how AI + crypto intersect. Building in public and writing more.
        </p>

        <h2>Links</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/miikey" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://twitter.com/miikey" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X / Twitter</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
